annotationA: NHP2-like protein 1 homolog; Binds to the 5'-stem-loop of U4 snRNA and may play a role in the late stage of spliceosome assembly. The protein undergoes a conformational change upon RNA-binding (By similarity)
annotationB: 28S ribosomal protein S7, mitochondrial; Structural constituent of ribosome; RNA binding. It is involved in the biological process described with: translation; Belongs to the universal ribosomal protein uS7 family
